summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plats 41E, 45E, 45W, pages 113, 119, 118 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in portions of the east 1/2 of Sec. 33, Twp. 25N, R. 4E W.M. and portions of the north 1/2 of Sec. 4, Twp. 24N, R. 4E W.M.
